data.description: Lots of great updates here including new roof in ‘23, new fence in ‘20, water heater in ‘21, garbage disposal  in ‘19, and four new commodes. This family home is situated on a cul-de-sac and  has just over 3200 sq. ft. of living space woth much to offer. Check out the amazing views from the living room. The entertainment center in the finished basement is sure to please. Just off the kitchen there is a covered patio wired to allow for a TV as well as a two tiered deck. Master suite and laundry are on the main floor with three beds and a full bath on the second floor. The lower level had tons of storage as well as two bonus rooms that may make exercise and office areas. With the addition of an egress window in the bonus room, this home could have five The pellet stove makes it warm in the winter downstairs. The built in bar and pellet stove stay. The backyard is fully fenced and has a storage shed.  There is an option to tie into natural gas at the street. In addition to the 2 car garage there is an addition parking pad. The seller will provide 3 months of home warranty coverage. No HOA here. Room sizes are approximate.
